biography: Martin is a highly accomplished golfer, a member of St. Laurence Golf, and a regular competitor in the prestigious Hector Trophée.

His consistent participation demonstrates a dedication to the tournament, having competed in the Hector Trophée in 2022, 2023, 2024, and 2025.  Martin's impressive track record includes a victory in the Hector Trophée in 2020, showcasing his skill and ability to perform under pressure.
Beyond his team success, Martin also claimed the individual Victor trophy at Hector Trophée VI, a testament to his exceptional talent and prowess on the course.
